  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43444</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_057_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あいつら……元気かな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I hope they're doing okay...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_057_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>子どもたちのことですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You mean the kids back in Totus?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43636</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_057_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、ああ……おかしいだろ。
まだここへ来てそれほど経ってないのに</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah, yeah...Sorry. Weird thing to think out loud after I've come all the way here, eh?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43760</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_057_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いえ……大切な人と離れ離れだと、
ほんのひと時でも、とても長く感じますね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No, it's okay. It's just normal to feel a little sad when we aren't close to loved ones.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43860</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_057_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだな……
あいつらを引き取って１年半か……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah...It's been a year and a half since I've started taking care of them.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43976</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_057_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>長いようで、短かく感じたのも、
あいつらとずっと一緒だったからか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's been a long time, but it really feels otherwise. All four of us have been always together.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_057_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>たった１年半であの子たち、
あんなに&lt;Chester&gt;さんを慕ってるんですね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Though it may not seem like much, I'm sure that year and half they got to know Mister &lt;Chester&gt; very well!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44172</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_057_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ガキのお守りは慣れてるからな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I grew used to babysit those brats!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44252</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_057_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Chester&gt;の頭がガキなんだろ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Maybe you've become a brat yourself!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44376</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_057_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おい！　こら！　自分で思ってても、
人に言われるとむかつくぞ、それは！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey! Don't jump into conversations like that or you'll really know me!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44484</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_057_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、そっか……
……アミィがいなくなってそんなに……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh...yeah...It's also about the time Ami's passed away...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44588</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_057_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あいつがいない時間は
１年にも１０年にも感じた……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>One year... ten years...It'll always feel the same without her...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44648</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_057_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
